{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"你研究了半天，就在研究这件事？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"假如说这些家具，这些酒菜，和那口棺材都是个叫好好先生的人送来的，那么这只猫一定也是他养的，所以……","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":146,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"所以怎么样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":148,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"那又怎么样呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"所以……","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"那么你还抱着它干什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"看来这只猫一定是母的，而且已经看上了你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"猫的记忆虽然不好，脑筋却很清楚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":186,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"脑筋清楚？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"它既然知道这里有鱼吃，为什么还要跑到别的地方去？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"但我又不是它的主人，它为什么要缠住我？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"你刚才喂它吃过一条鱼，是不是？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"谁喂它吃鱼，谁就是它的主人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":198,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker