{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"你根本不必送这些东西来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"你们帮了我很多忙，我总不能不表示一点心意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":306,"line_end":306},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"但这些东西我们还是不能收。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"因为……因为你是女人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"女人也是人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"她说话的口气倒跟你差不多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"男人送这么多东西来，我们也一样不能收。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"那就要租金。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"我付。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"还要保管费。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"我也付。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"每天十两银子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"要先付，不能欠账。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"我先付十天行不行？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"你有病？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"有病？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"不但有病，而且病很重。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":364,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"我吃又吃得下，睡又睡得着，怎么会有病呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"也许你这病就是吃多了胀出来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"你信不信？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"若连他都不信，只怕天下就没有别的人会信了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"所以我也没有这么样说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"你准备怎么样说？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":390,"line_end":390},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text"