{"segment":6,"line_start":501,"line_end":600,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"你做事的确比很多男人还像男人，譬如说……","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"你认为女人常会无缘无故的生气？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"其实男人并不如他们自己想得那么聪明。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"那时他就会知道究竟是谁聪明了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":530,"line_end":530},{"speaker":"char_suan_mei_tang","speaker_name":"酸梅汤","listener":null,"text":"其实一个男人能有点姑娘腔也不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":544,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":546,"line_end":546},{"speaker":"char_wang_dong","speaker_name":"王动","listener":null,"text":"你是男人？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"你来干什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":570,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"来聊聊。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"你好像不太喜欢她。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"喜欢她的人已经够多了，用不着我再去凑数。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":580,"line_end":580},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"今天下午，你们好像聊得很开心嘛。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":584,"line_end":584},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":13,"line_start":586,"line_end":586},{"speaker":"char_yan_qi","speaker_name":"燕七","listener":null,"text":"既然聊得那么开心，何必来找我？","tone":"